name: Machine Learning
description:
The "Machine Learning" playlist is a comprehensive collection of videos designed to help anyone learn the basics of machine learning and its various applications.

In this playlist, you'll find a wide range of topics, including the fundamentals of machine learning, data preparation, model building, and evaluation. You'll also discover how machine learning is being used in various industries, such as healthcare, finance, and marketing.

Each video in the playlist is presented in an easy-to-follow format, with clear explanations and examples to help you grasp the key concepts. Whether you're new to machine learning or looking to expand your knowledge, this playlist will provide you with a solid foundation to build upon.
